  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK639">
<l>paḻuteṇṇu mantiriyiṟ pakkattuṭ ṭevva </l>
<l> reḻupatu kōṭi yuṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Far better are seventy crores of enemies (for a king) than a minister at his side who intends (his) ruin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
